<title>USA: DDJ Group holds 7.47 pct stake in Hills.</title>
<headline>DDJ Group holds 7.47 pct stake in Hills.</headline>
<dateline>WASHINGTON 1996-08-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>A group led by DDJ Capital Management LLC and its affiliates said Friday it held a 7.47 percent stake in Hills Stores Co, or 761,634 common shares.</p>
<p>In a filing with the Securities and Exchange Commission, DDJ said its stake included net purchases of 375,900 shares between July 1 and August 16. The price per share breakdown was not given.</p>
<p>The group said it bought the shares for specific investment objectives established by investors in the group.</p>
